'''Harpy's Gold''' is a type of flower that exists in the region of [[Slaver's Bay]] on the continent of [[Essos]].

Harpy's Gold is attractive, but unlike [[Dusk Rose|Dusk Roses]] it cannot be used to make tea, because it is poisonous.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Two Swords]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
